title: You Lyin' and the Truth Ain't in You
description:
Swagu and Perk discuss Joel Embiid and Aaron Rodgers testing positive for COVID, Russell Westbrook needing to lock in with the Lakers, why consistency is the key to greatness, the Astroworld tragedy, a dirty play by a QB, and what they're about to have for dinner. Let's get it!
